{"title":"郝帅栋的日常","slug":"run","date":"2022-10-18T17:19:57.458Z","updated":"2022-10-18T17:19:57.466Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/run.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":null,"covers":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"郝帅栋的日常\"><a href=\"#郝帅栋的日常\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"郝帅栋的日常\"></a><em><strong>郝帅栋</strong></em>的日常</h1><hr>\n<p> ! <a href=\"../run.jpeg\" title=\"润总牛逼\">润总</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"早上\"><a href=\"#早上\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"早上\"></a>早上</h2><ul>\n<li><em>郝帅栋</em>睡到早上九点</li>\n<li><em>郝帅栋</em>会被润总叫醒去买饭</li>\n<li><em>郝帅栋</em>在买完饭请润总吃饭</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"中午\"><a href=\"#中午\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"中午\"></a>中午</h2><ul>\n<li><em>郝帅栋</em>为润总买饭</li>\n<li><em>郝帅栋</em>为润总买饮料</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"下午\"><a href=\"#下午\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下午\"></a>下午</h2><ul>\n<li><em>郝帅栋</em>请润总起床</li>\n<li><em>郝帅栋</em>请润总出去玩，润总不去</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"晚上\"><a href=\"#晚上\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"晚上\"></a>晚上</h2><ul>\n<li><em>郝帅栋</em>为润总买饮料</li>\n<li>*郝帅栋为润总买泡面</li>\n</ul>\n","categories":[],"tags":[]}